name: Meeeting_R
query:
Select a.name as "Meeeting:Link/Meeeting:120",
        a.date as "Date:date/Date:120",
        a.status as "Status::120",
        a.from_time as "From Time:date/From Time:100",
        a.to_time as "To Time:date/To Time:100",
        b.assigned_to as "Assigned To:Link/User:100",
        b.complete_by as "Complete By:date/Complete By:100",
        b.description as "Description:Text/:150"
    from `tabMeeeting` a join `tabMeeeting Minute` b
    where b.parent=a.name;
